%F A265185 a(n) = 2 * ((2 + sqrt(2))^n + (2 - sqrt(2))^n) = Sum_{k=0..3} 2^(2n) (cos((2k+1)*Pi/8))^(2n) = 2*2^(2n) (cos(Pi/8)^(2n) + cos(3*Pi/8)^(2n)) = 2 Sum_{k=0..1} (exp(i(2k+1)*Pi/8) + exp(-i*(2k+1)*Pi/8))^(2n).
%F A265185 E.g.f.: 2 * e^(2*x) * (e^(sqrt(2)*x) + e^(-sqrt(2)*x)) = 4*e^(2*x)*cosh(sqrt(2)*x) = 2*(exp(4*x*cos(Pi/8)^2) + exp(4*x cos(3*Pi/8)^2) ).
%F A265185 a(n) = 4*A006012(n) = 8*A007052(n-1) = 2*A056236(n).
%F A265185 G.f.: (4-8*x)/(1-4*x+2*x^2). - _Robert Israel_, Dec 07 2015
%F A265185 Note the preceding o.g.f. is four times that of A006012 and the denominator is y^4 * A127672(4,1/y) with y = sqrt(x). Compare this with those of A025192 and A189315. - _Tom Copeland_, Dec 08 2015
